data.text: @realityblurred Even finding out about the relationship was charming. Everyone knew about Gabby’s, but these two flew under the radar. I found this whole season satisfying. Great storytelling, entertainment and a great top 5+!
@realityblurred Yeah: the condensed performance period impacted our ability to connect to the performers, but it’s nice to know they got close.
Not the relationship—the way the eliminated singers all joined in the celebration and singing.
@realityblurred That’s a funny way to spell underwhelming.
